    Jet^3(H) adds C(6,3) = 20 components, total = 42
    Jet^4(H) adds C(6,4) = 15 components, total = 57
    Jet^5(H) adds C(6,5) = 6 components, total = 63
    ... Jet^6(H) = full function, total = 2^6 = 64

